\c 35
\s Mwari haanzwi kuchema kwavanhu nokuda kokusatenda kwavo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Erihu akapindurawo, akati:
\p
\v 2 Munoti ndiko kururama kwenyu here. Munoti, kururama kwangu kunopfuura kwaMwari?
\v 3 Zvamunoti: Muchabatsirweiko nazvo? Ndichawaneiko, zvingapfuura zvandingawana kana ndatadza hangu?
\v 4 Ndichakupindurai, pamwe chete neshamwari dzenyu.
\v 5 Tarirai kudenga-denga, muone; tarirai makore okudenga akakwirira kupfuura imi.
\v 6 Kana muchinge matadza, ko mungamuitei iye? Kana kudarika kwenyu kuchinge kwakawanda, ko mungamuitei?
\v 7 Kana makarurama, mungamupeiko? Kana iye uchapiweiko paruoko rwenyu?
\v 8 Kuipa kwenyu kunobata munhu akaita semi, kururama kwenyu kungabatsira mwanakomana womunhu.
\v 9 Vanhu vanoridza mhere nokuda kokumanikidza kwakawanda; vanoridza mhere kuti varwirwe paruoko rwoane simba.
\v 10 Asi hapana anoti, Mwari muiti wangu aripiko? Iye anotiimbisa usiku;
\v 11 uye anotidzidzisa kupfuura shiri dzokudenga? Anotiita vakachenjera kupfuura shiri dzokudenga?
\v 12 Ipapo vanochema, asi hapana anopindura, nokuda kokuzvikudza kwavanhu vakaipa.
\v 13 Zvirokwazvo Mwari haanganzwi zvisina maturo, Wemasimbaose haangavi nehanya nazvo.
\p
\v 14 Ndoda kana muchiti: Handimuoni; mhosva iri pamberi pake, chimumirirai henyu!
\v 15 Asi zvino, zvaasina kutsiva pakutsamwa kwake, kana kusava nehanya zvikuru nokuzvikudza;
\v 16 naizvozvo Jobho woshamisa muromo wake achireva zvisina maturo; wowanza mashoko asingazivi.
